title: JarExporter causes out of sync message when overwriting exported jar file
description: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported jar in the same directory (project), if you overwrite the exported jar file for the second time, an out of sync message is displayed.
OB: Exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported jar in the same directory (project)
EB: Out of sync message displayed when overwriting the exported jar file for the second time
